hi again



Pleasantly that you have answered my letter.



It is interesting to me and it is fascinating to write letters to too time to the stranger.



I hope that it is temporarily unfamiliar. I think that in due course we can learn each other better.



Tell to me about itself. What yours hobbies? Where do you live and than you are engaged? How you look?



I with pleasure shall read it from you.



I shall tell shortly about myself. I was born in small village Iliynka on October, 23, 1979. Studied in high school. When to me 17 years I were executed has gone to city Yoshkar-Ola to enter the university. Has acted and has remained in city. Studied as the bookkeeper. Now I work as the bookkeeper in small firm. It is a lot of work but it only is pleasant to me.



My mum lives in village. The father already for a long time is not present. I to visit my mum each days off. I very much love her.



At leisure I like to visit employment on aerobics. Also in the childhood I was engaged in track and field athletics. Was the candidate for the master of sports on running.



But unfortunately now I am not engaged in it because absolutely there is no time because of work.



Every morning I like to wake up at 6.00 and to make small jog on park near to my house. I live in an apartment which to me the firm rented.



I live one.



I certainly had friends but it is not serious. I want the greater. I want to see the world and to understand as people abroad live.



I like to prepare. I to this was learned since the childhood by my mum.



It is pleasant to spend time in the good company.



Never drink alcoholic drinks. Only certainly at university I presumed a few beer. But now is not present. Never smoked and I am not going to smoke.



I like a healthy way of life. I believe that it allows me to feel like always well and cheerful mood.



My biggest passion is utensils. I like to collect various utensils. It is a lot of crystal.



My motto it: never to cry and always to go forward.



It certainly sounds a little courageously. But I such. Has got used to achieve all.



In the man I appreciate first of all mind, beauty not only external but also internal. Also care and fidelity. Trust and honesty. Optimism and love. Reliability and softness to the loving person.



For these reasons I could not find yet the suitable person for myself. Many men tried to have with me acquaintance but character traits do not allow me to answer them mutually.



It only brief representation about itself.



I hope that you still will write to me.



Elena

I have the main belief that it is necessary to be upset never and always to be with fine mood.



Describe to me the feelings which you you test at any bad news. It is a press, frustration, a pain or affliction. As you pass all this.



I had many pains in the life. It when I have arrived one to the big city. Did not know that to me to do and made many mistakes. There was a pain when my father has died. A pain of the first parting with the favourite person. All this was. But I already know that it is impossible to return time back. Only to make visibility of the past.



The person this such essence which is capable to study only on mistakes. These are or another's.
